N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 460.6 - Notification of approval or disapproval of application for self-insurance

State Regulations

The bureau shall notify the applicant in writing of
approval or disapproval of the application for self-insurance and all facts
pertinent thereto. Notes
